text: Ui Yah-tor (born 10 October 1938) is a Taiwanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Taiwan Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
